Three explosions unleashed by suspected suicide bombers
devastated a central Jerusalem pedestrian area close to a crowded
cafe and bank shortly after 3:00 p.m. local time. The Muslim
fundamentalist group Hamas was reported to have claimed
responsibility for the attack.
</P>
<P>
The incident occurred one month after another deadly bomb
attack at a nearby market in Jerusalem. 
