also do everything in order that the peace process itself would
not be the victim of terrorism too,'' said Chirac.
</P>
<P>
He said that the only response to terrorism is to ``relaunch
the peace process with determination.''
</P>
<P>
``That will allow, I am convinced, to ensure to all sides
security and open the perspectives of hope to the peoples of the
region,'' he added. 
