Africa Travel Market Exhibition set to open in Nairobi and
Johannesburg late this month, local press reported today.
</P>
<P>
The exhibition will kick off with a two-day first-ever Africa
Travel Market Conference here from September 15 to 16 and then in
Johannesburg, South Africa from September 18 to 21.
</P>
