<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 5 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
today fell 7 HK dollars to close at 2,977 HK dollars a tael,
according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers in Hong
Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 322.65 dollars a troy ounce,
down 0.72 HK dollars from the previous close at today's exchange
rate of one U.S. dollar to 7.7450 HK dollars. 
</P>
</TEXT>
