<HEADLINE> Thai Bourse Index Up 18.19 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, September 5 (Xinhua) -- The Stock Exchange of Thailand
(SET) index today rose 18.19 points to close at 540.39.
</P>
<P>
Some 134.3 million shares worth 3.3 billion baht (86.8 million
U.S. dollars) changed hands today.
</P>
<P>
The SET index Thursday gained 8.13 points to close at 522.2,
with shares worth 3.536 billion baht (117.9 million dollars)
traded. 
</P>
</TEXT>
