<HEADLINE> Sri Lanka to Get Modern Equipment for Trawlers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, September 5 (Xinhua) -- Sri Lanka is to implement a
2.1 million U.S. dollar project to provide modern equipment for
600 trawlers owned by fishermen in the Southern province,
